1
00:00:00,240 --> 00:00:01,240
I know.

2
00:00:01,880 --> 00:00:04,000
I have to stop her.

3
00:00:04,000 --> 00:00:05,120
From getting her revenge.

4
00:00:05,320 --> 00:00:06,320
But...

5
00:00:07,200 --> 00:00:09,480
Even if it's just for a moment,
I want to be with her.

6
00:00:10,080 --> 00:00:11,080
Even if it's all for revenge.

7
00:00:11,080 --> 00:00:12,080
Just being together...

8
00:00:12,600 --> 00:00:13,840
Even if revenge is all that connects us...

9
00:00:13,840 --> 00:00:14,840
As long as I can be with her...

10
00:00:15,440 --> 00:00:16,480
I don't care.

11
00:00:23,120 --> 00:00:24,600
Just to be by her side.

12
00:00:24,920 --> 00:00:26,480
Destiny.

13
00:00:27,040 --> 00:00:28,760
My first love.

14
00:00:30,080 --> 00:00:32,120
And probably my only love.

15
00:00:32,640 --> 00:00:34,640
If she can't
find happiness...

16
00:00:36,520 --> 00:00:37,520
Then...

17
00:00:38,000 --> 00:00:39,000
I have to let go.

18
00:00:40,640 --> 00:00:42,120
I have to endure it.

19
00:00:42,600 --> 00:00:44,400
And end this quickly.

20
00:00:51,440 --> 00:00:52,440
What are you doing here?
